metadata.name: Memesterpieces Checks Printer
metadata.description:
Memesterpieces Checks Printer Edition

First burn will be occuring RIGHT AWAY after the mint period ends.

- Opening up for public on 16th February, 12 pm UTC

Exclusive for these VisualizeValue editions holders:  
(Snapshot was taken on 3:45 am, 15th February 2023)  
- Checks VV Edition - 2 per wallet  
- Checks VV Originals - 2 per wallet  
- Netvvork - 4 per wallet  
- VV Rare - 4 per wallet  
- Characters - 4 per wallet  
- Merge VV ( SOON ) - 1 per wallet


Memestepieces Printer is an ERC-1155 NFT from Checks Museum by Memesterpieces, consisting of 200+ Arts.  
Arts that we will have in this collection are Posters, Banners, Wallpapers, etc.


Feel free to use your burn and claim arts later with burn mechanisms. You can do whatever you want. For example, frame it.

All burn mechanisms and links for Memesterpieces Checks Museum will be posted in @CalvinStephh Twitter page.
